    lessonInLife:
      "The great spiritual lesson of Cancer is learning that true security comes from within, that the home they have been searching for their entire life lives inside their own heart, and that their capacity to love is not a vulnerability but a superpower. They are here to learn that impermanence does not negate meaning — that the fact that all things change does not make them any less precious. Cancer's deepest spiritual work is releasing the grip of fear and opening fully to the flow of life, trusting that the same love that sustains them will also sustain those they care for, even in their absence.",
